data.description: Looking for a home with an in-law or teenager suite or just a separate living area to rent for airbnb? Want a 3-car garage for all your vehicles, toys, and tinkering? This one is for you. Wonderful 4 bedroom 3 bath home in the heart of Hixson. Only minutes to downtown and close to everything Hixson has to offer. Lovely, established subdivision with large lots unique homes. No cookie-cutters here. Recently updated with new flooring and paint among other upgrades. Master is on the main along with two other bedrooms and two bathrooms. Gorgeous open living room and kitchen with stone fireplace to really draw the eyes. One set of laundry is upstairs and another downstairs.Finished basement includes what could be a second master bedroom, full bath, living room/den with a separate entrance. There is also a kitchenette and tons of extra space to make your own. Don't miss this hidden gem in one of Hixson's best subdivisions.
